{"tid":752462,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有村架純家姐影水着寫真　因乜事成身忌廉？","createTime":"2018-07-22T23:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T04:22:03.000Z","uid":1426,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fb27178cfdc008fe792f14c1a6b1bf97d162f9fa","tid":752462,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T23:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180722/photo/bkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180722175436\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180722%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180722175436&h=380cd346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有村架純(圓圖)的水着女家姐有村藍里，被NTV的電視節目大整蠱。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n25歲日本當紅女星有村架純，最近忙於拍攝TBS電視台的10月新劇，在改編自同名漫畫的《中學聖日記》中，大玩師生戀橋段，叫外界相當關注能否超越松嶋菜菜子與瀧澤秀明的經典師生戀劇集《魔女的條件》。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂有村架純的27歲水着女家姐有村藍里，今年4月為網劇首度挑戰做女優，令她對演員工作更感興趣，還視石原聰美為目標。雖然如此，有村藍里暫時仍然主攻綜藝節目界，近日她便成為NTV整蠱節目的目標，被騙到泳池拍水着寫真，期間卻遭諧星中岡創一從後偷襲，向她噴射忌廉大炮，弄得全身都是忌廉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180722/photo/bkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001_02b.jpg?20180722175436\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180722%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20180722175436&h=8cf62fcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有村藍里被安排到泳池邊拍水着寫真。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180722/photo/bkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001_03b.jpg?20180722175436\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180722%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20180722175436&h=0dd34aec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點會係只影相咁簡單。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180722/photo/bkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001_04b.jpg?20180722175436\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180722%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20180722175436&h=3ccb7d9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n節目安排諧星中岡創一從後偷襲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180722/photo/bkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001_05b.jpg?20180722175436\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180722%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20180722175436&h=bdee18bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中岡創一向有村藍里發射忌廉炮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180722/photo/bkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001_06b.jpg?20180722175436\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180722%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20180722175436&h=e5f0b194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n靚妝冇喇！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180722/photo/bkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001_07b.jpg?20180722175436\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180722%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20180722175436&h=64d5d4b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n慘慘豬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180722/bkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180722%2Fbkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001.html&d=36Rt6SDeh3uDv2hevI%2BaVzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=d031a1d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180722/bkn-20180722171446331-0722_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/073047_b210d9f3c450efc9f1eeb383bece4999.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F073047_b210d9f3c450efc9f1e